@DarthParallax   

That won't be the case as far as colour identity goes. The black/white hybrid mana symbol on extort cards is in the reminder text, and is not part of the card's actual colour identity.  

If that were the case, the original printing of [Trinisphere](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Trinisphere) would only be usable in mono black decks.
